{"id": 556, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x奥迪】你想要什么样的旅行车？", "description": "最好一站式解决我“想走就走”“想带谁走就带谁走”“想去哪就去哪”的需求。", "record_count": 1986, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145054yqU6IlQS74dxfmbX.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-24T18:11:41Z", "options": [{"id": 12801, "content": "要足够大大大大的车厢空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142896}, {"id": 12802, "content": "空间够大", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196463}, {"id": 12803, "content": "车震时车不会摇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196480}, {"id": 12804, "content": "后会无期那种哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146452}, {"id": 13828, "content": "变形金刚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212059}, {"id": 40964, "content": "呼呼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 420722}, {"id": 12805, "content": "我要狂拽酷炫哪炸天的旅行车?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43073}, {"id": 12811, "content": "有弹射装备（别问我什么时候用", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55088}, {"id": 12813, "content": "空间大，可自动导航，及有一定保护措施的", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195533}, {"id": 12815, "content": "不能优雅的放置自行车的旅行车不是好car", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145609}, {"id": 12816, "content": "能在里面普通家里的床上那样舒舒服服的睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196604}, {"id": 12818, "content": "带上我的大玩具，自行车或别的什么，去我想去的地方玩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172778}, {"id": 12821, "content": "想带爸妈一起旅行，最希望能缩短路上时间，有个随意门打开就到地方啦，节省路上的时间！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196741}, {"id": 12822, "content": "30万以内的旅行车", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196810}, {"id": 12824, "content": "太阳能发电，不用加油，可以储水净化用水，车厢有睡觉和喝咖啡，还有卫生间，看风景和发呆的地方，车身不要太大，像头等舱舒适，要便宜些实用些，能像游艇水里游，没有这功能也没关系……能长途跋涉就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 182987}, {"id": 12826, "content": "逼格要高", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144949rxc5wPS2uz4YMHE9.jpg", "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195557}, {"id": 12828, "content": "依靠车震为前进动力的永动机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196950}, {"id": 12830, "content": "自动洗车系统", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196971}, {"id": 12831, "content": "\n\n还有自动除去车里烟味就是关着门也可以抽烟但车里仍然没有味", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196971}, {"id": 12832, "content": "在往车里配个小秘书系统！解决一系列的难题～还可以聊天用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196971}, {"id": 13090, "content": "重要的是有个男朋友或女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202005}, {"id": 12837, "content": "飘的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197056}, {"id": 12839, "content": "无忧无虑，自动导航", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197191}, {"id": 16424, "content": "ssmart", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245375}, {"id": 12842, "content": "后排可伸缩空间且车内设置合理的置物空间设计", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197211}, {"id": 15417, "content": "能飞能跑，还会自动驾驶的车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129288}, {"id": 13372, "content": "不要有汽油味，睡觉时能自动防盗防破坏还能味道户外清幽花草香。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205945}, {"id": 14396, "content": "七座猎装轿跑，车高有骐达那么高，二排座腿部空间有五系加长那么大，最重要的是！后两排座位放平可以当成大双人（PS；轮包处是个小床头桌就更好了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220380}, {"id": 13373, "content": "走到哪里都可以上网", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205945}, {"id": 15178, "content": "能上山，能下海，有速度，有空间，天窗必需全景，外形靠进概念", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232230}, {"id": 14923, "content": "忘我地融入自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228702}, {"id": 14926, "content": "便宜耐用毛病少多拉快跑不费油", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228721}, {"id": 13395, "content": "撞了车以后座子能弹射", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 206353}, {"id": 13143, "content": "一边跟闺蜜或者男朋友或者陌生人聊天一边旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202985}, {"id": 12892, "content": "有奥迪的旅行", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235036WeM2oIZR9BPTALCz.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197513}, {"id": 15454, "content": "车内隔音，音响要好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234767}, {"id": 12896, "content": "目前只要求单反", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161938}, {"id": 12897, "content": "空间利用率大，省油", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197573}, {"id": 13410, "content": "漫无目的出游它却最懂你带你去的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193314}, {"id": 12905, "content": "用核能当能源，一辈子不需要其他动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197665}, {"id": 16745, "content": "房车嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246421}, {"id": 14701, "content": "大马力四驱，七座舒适，比如rs6", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225179}, {"id": 15473, "content": "上的了天 下的了地 潜的了水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217385}, {"id": 13941, "content": "我想带个媳妇的车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213727}, {"id": 15230, "content": "一辆房车，环游世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232305}, {"id": 16766, "content": "每个座位都能平躺当床的车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214667}, {"id": 12927, "content": "房车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196077}, {"id": 12929, "content": "大空间，安全", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196170}, {"id": 13441, "content": "经济实用就好，比如北京B40。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207266}, {"id": 12935, "content": "空间大\n内饰好\n降噪音\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195872}]}